snippet.title: GRIME | Game Intro Reveal
snippet.description:
ESRB Rated: TEEN for Animated Blood, Fantasy Violence
Coming soon to PC!

Crush your foes with living weapons and consume their essence with your sentient black hole! GRIME is a fast and unforgiving soulslike metroidvania coming soon to PC Platforms. Take a look at the opening few moments of GRIME for the first time ever! 

To learn more about GRIME, Clover Bite, or Akupara Games, visit:
►GRIME: https://linktr.ee/playgrime
►Clover Bite: https://www.grimegame.com/​
►Akupara Games: http://linktr.ee/akuparagames
